---------------
EMA = weight * price + (1-weight) * EMA(prev)      // "weigth" = "alpha"
or
EMA = EMA(prev) + weight * (price-EMA(prev))
                                                   // @see  https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moving_average#Approximating_the_EMA_with_a_limited_number_of_terms
